{"tid":1416834,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"與其叫佢地做「狗」,不如直接叫「畜牲」啦","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:37:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:12:25.000Z","uid":209873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ca66111cc4b67cb8ea65cc36be5f6e0e48535eed","tid":1416834,"uid":209873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:37:49.000Z","msg":"雖然變咗兩隻字， 有時講嘢係麻煩啲，但「畜生」兩隻字聽落比「狗」更有侮辱性又有力， 唔知大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋呢排見兄弟搞宿舍先領悟到，比起搞佢哋個竇，搞宿舍真係更聰明嘅做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞佢哋個竇佢哋不痛不癢，仲可以被罷工，<br />\n搞佢哋屋企就唔同啦，禍必及妻兒，搞到班畜牲嘅老婆仔女好似比黑社會收債咁，街又唔敢落，屋企又唔等返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8263dd20a2f85fd113df6364d2c7d5177943d9a7","tid":1416834,"uid":52192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:01:56.000Z","msg":"侮辱左畜牲"},{"pid":"52067efce176d7c9fe55ea06cfbdb8d3a6af4c24","tid":1416834,"uid":209873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8263dd20a2f85fd113df6364d2c7d5177943d9a7","tid":1416834,"uid":52192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:01:56.000Z","msg":"侮辱左畜牲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:10:28.000Z","msg":"諗諗下其實叫咩都係侮辱咗嗰樣嘢，話唔定黑警先係最低賤嘅名詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de206694c22dced91ee15c4d51d0343f04c78693","tid":1416834,"uid":52192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52067efce176d7c9fe55ea06cfbdb8d3a6af4c24","tid":1416834,"uid":209873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8263dd20a2f85fd113df6364d2c7d5177943d9a7","tid":1416834,"uid":52192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:01:56.000Z","msg":"侮辱左畜牲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:10:28.000Z","msg":"諗諗下其實叫咩都係侮辱咗嗰樣嘢，話唔定黑警先係最低賤嘅名詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.g